      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0643P0-05630'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0643P0_20030129_GCR_120' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 60 [<span class="italic">Appeal against disqualification</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0643P0-05631'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0643P0_20030129_GCR_121' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
